trans-unit.source: Extends design-time behavior for the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Repeater" /> control.
Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.RepeaterDesigner" /> class.
Gets the action list collection for the control designer.
A <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListCollection" /> object that contains the <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList" /> items for the control designer.
trans-unit.target: 컨트롤 디자이너에 대한 <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList" /> 항목을 포함하는 <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListCollection" /> 개체입니다.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the name of a specific table or view in the data source object to bind the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Repeater" /> control to.
The name of a table or view in the data source.
trans-unit.target: 테이블 또는 뷰의 데이터 원본에서의 이름입니다.

trans-unit.source: A data-binding expression that identifies the source of data for the associated <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Repeater" /> control.
A data binding expression.
Provides access to the associated designer component for the data source.
An <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Design.IDataSourceDesigner" /> object.
Gets or sets the <see cref="P:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Repeater.DataSourceID" /> property of the associated control.
The ID of the associated control's data source control.
trans-unit.target: 연결된 된 컨트롤의 데이터 소스 컨트롤의 ID입니다.

trans-unit.source: Gets the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerDataSourceView" /> object associated with the data source of this designer.
The <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerDataSourceView" /> associated with the data source of this designer.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerDataSourceView" /> 이 디자이너의 데이터 원본과 연결 합니다.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> to release both the managed and unmanaged resources; <see langword="false" /> to release only the unmanaged resources.
Releases the unmanaged resources used by the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.RepeaterDesigner" /> object and optionally releases the managed resources.

When the disposing parameter is `true`, the `Dispose` method releases all the resources held by the managed objects that this <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.RepeaterDesigner> object references.
trans-unit.target: Disposing 매개 변수 인 경우 `true`, `Dispose` 메서드 관리 개체가 보유 하는 모든 리소스를 해제 합니다.이 <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.RepeaterDesigner> 개체에서 참조 합니다.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="M:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.RepeaterDesigner.Dispose(System.Boolean)" /> method can be called multiple times by other objects.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="M:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.RepeaterDesigner.Dispose(System.Boolean)" /> 메서드는 다른 개체에서 여러 번 호출할 수 있습니다.

trans-unit.source: When overriding it, ensure that you do not reference objects that have been disposed in an earlier call to <see cref="M:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.RepeaterDesigner.Dispose(System.Boolean)" />.
trans-unit.target: 멤버 함수를 재정의 하는 경우 확인 한 이전 호출에서 삭제 된 개체를 참조 하지 않도록 <see cref="M:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.RepeaterDesigner.Dispose(System.Boolean)" />합니다.

trans-unit.source: For more information about how to implement this method, see [Implementing a Dispose Method](~/docs/standard/garbage-collection/implementing-dispose.md).
trans-unit.target: 이 메서드를 구현 하는 방법에 대 한 자세한 내용은 참조 [Dispose 메서드를 구현](~/docs/standard/garbage-collection/implementing-dispose.md)합니다.

trans-unit.source: For more information about the Dispose and Finalize methods, see [Dispose Pattern](~/docs/standard/design-guidelines/dispose-pattern.md).
trans-unit.target: Dispose 및 Finalize 방법에 대 한 자세한 내용은 참조 [Dispose 패턴](~/docs/standard/design-guidelines/dispose-pattern.md)합니다.

trans-unit.source: Called by a design host such as [!INCLUDE[vsprvslong](~/includes/vsprvslong-md.md)] after a user selects a data source at design time.
This method is available for derived classes that require additional processing after a user selects a data source at design time.
trans-unit.target: 이 메서드는 사용자가 디자인 타임에 데이터 소스를 선택한 후에 추가로 처리 해야 하는 파생된 클래스에 사용할 수 있습니다.

trans-unit.source: Returns design-time sample data.
The minimum number of rows of sample data that the data source should contain.
Returns design-time sample data based on the <see cref="M:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.RepeaterDesigner.GetResolvedSelectedDataSource" /> method and using the specified number of rows.
An <see cref="T:System.Collections.IEnumerable" /> object containing sample data for use at design time.
An <see cref="T:System.Collections.IEnumerable" /> object containing data to use in creating similar sample data at design time.
The minimum number of rows of sample data that the data source should contain.
Returns design-time sample data based on the provided data and using the specified number of rows.
An <see cref="T:System.Collections.IEnumerable" /> object containing sample data for use at design time.
Retrieves the HTML markup to be used for the design-time representation of the control.
Design-time HTML markup.
Retrieves the HTML markup to represent a Web server control at design time that will have no visual representation at run time.
The HTML markup used to represent a control at design time that would otherwise have no visual representation.
The default is a rectangle that contains the type and ID of the component.
The exception that occurred.
Retrieves the HTML markup that provides information about the specified exception.
The design-time HTML markup for the specified exception.
Gets the selected data member from the selected data source.
An <see cref="T:System.Collections.IEnumerable" /> that contains a collection of values used to supply design-time data.
The default value is <see langword="null" />.

The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.RepeaterDesigner.GetResolvedSelectedDataSource%2A> method uses the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.RepeaterDesigner.GetSelectedDataSource%2A> method to construct a data source from the object that is specified by the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.RepeaterDesigner.DataSource%2A> and <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.RepeaterDesigner.DataMember%2A> properties.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.RepeaterDesigner.GetResolvedSelectedDataSource%2A> 메서드는 <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.RepeaterDesigner.GetSelectedDataSource%2A> 변수로 지정 된 개체에서 데이터 소스를 생성 하는 메서드는 <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.RepeaterDesigner.DataSource%2A> 및 <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.RepeaterDesigner.DataMember%2A> 속성입니다.

trans-unit.source: Retrieves the selected data source component from the container of the associated <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Repeater" /> control.
The selected data source; <see langword="null" /> if a data source is not found or if a data source with the selected name does not exist.

The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.RepeaterDesigner.GetSelectedDataSource%2A> method uses the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignTimeData.GetSelectedDataSource%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> method to construct a data source from the object that is specified by the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.RepeaterDesigner.DataSource%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.RepeaterDesigner.GetSelectedDataSource%2A> 메서드는 <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignTimeData.GetSelectedDataSource%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> 변수로 지정 된 개체에서 데이터 소스를 생성 하는 메서드는 <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.RepeaterDesigner.DataSource%2A> 속성입니다.

trans-unit.source: The associated <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Repeater" /> control.
Initializes the designer with the provided <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Repeater" /> control.
The source of the event.
The event data.
Called when the associated control changes.
Handles changes made to the data source
The properties for the class of the component.
Filters the properties to replace the runtime data source property descriptor with the designer's property descriptor.
Gets a value indicating whether the associated control has any templates defined.
A value that indicates whether any templates are defined for the associated control.
trans-unit.target: 연결된 된 컨트롤에 대 한 모든 템플릿은 정의 되어 있는지 여부를 나타내는 값입니다.
